4a1b886b-913e-4aad-b5b6-6e41b0db23a6.title: Bearing
4a1b886b-913e-4aad-b5b6-6e41b0db23a6.description: Everything you place on the bearing will revolve. Bearings can also be connected to an engine or the driver's seat to be controlled in different ways.

aa8d89eb-919b-42f4-8b58-af6f0d5856bc.title: Sport Suspension
aa8d89eb-919b-42f4-8b58-af6f0d5856bc.description: Adds bounce and stability. Great for vehicles to prevent them from easily tipping over. This suspension is small, but has a firmer bounce.

a481138b-fae9-47c9-9bc2-91b6d2e2bf52.title: Off-Road Suspension
a481138b-fae9-47c9-9bc2-91b6d2e2bf52.description: Adds bounce and stability. Great for vehicles to prevent them from easily tipping over. This suspension has a lot of bounce, making it ideal for off-road vehicles.

260b4597-f1ac-409c-8e6b-90c998c5fe94.title: Piston
260b4597-f1ac-409c-8e6b-90c998c5fe94.description: Extends and contracts! Connect it to a trigger to activate. The piston can also be connected to a controller to make it extend and contract in a sequence. Perfect for creating impressive creations.

d5e36413-b3c1-4636-8447-3410c352ec7b.title: Gas Engine
d5e36413-b3c1-4636-8447-3410c352ec7b.description: An engine with fixed speed and adjustable power, ideally suited to powering vehicles. Can be connected to a driver's seat or triggers.

cf3fdcfc-a7e5-4497-b000-ffda67dd8db7.title: Driver's Seat
cf3fdcfc-a7e5-4497-b000-ffda67dd8db7.description: Makes bearings turn left and right. Can be connected to an engine to control the direction of travel. Can also be connected to triggers that can be activated from the seat.

5e96037a-a338-490a-a76f-6b4d820f8e46.title: Thruster
5e96037a-a338-490a-a76f-6b4d820f8e46.description: Enough of these can make things fly. Needs to be connected to a trigger or the driverâ€™s seat in order to activate.

12862001-666c-4bdd-8326-a1f43610d28b.title: Controller
12862001-666c-4bdd-8326-a1f43610d28b.description: Allows bearings to rotate in sequence. Perfect for building transforming creations. Needs to be connected to bearings. Activated by connecting a trigger or driver's seat to the controller.

1e8d93a4-506b-470d-9ada-9c0a321e2db5.title: Button
1e8d93a4-506b-470d-9ada-9c0a321e2db5.description: Activates stuff. The button activates as long as it remains pressed

6546c293-a5aa-4442-80d5-a2819f077746.title: Electric Engine
6546c293-a5aa-4442-80d5-a2819f077746.description: Powers bearings. An engine with fixed power and adjustable speed. A slow engine with a lot of strength. Can be connected to a driverâ€™s seat or triggers.

add3acc6-a6fd-44e8-a384-a7a16ce13c81.title: Sensor
add3acc6-a6fd-44e8-a384-a7a16ce13c81.description: It detects, it activates! The sensor activates when detecting any kind of surface that comes into its view, and has a reach of ten blocks. It can activate an engine, a thruster, the controller and more.

7cf717d7-d167-4f2d-a6e7-6b2c70aa3986.title: Switch
7cf717d7-d167-4f2d-a6e7-6b2c70aa3986.description: Unlimited toggling on demand. The Switch activates whatever itâ€™s connected to, making it indispensible when you want to turn things on and off with a single push. It can activate an engine, a thruster, the controller and more.

ed27f5e2-cac5-4a32-a5d9-49f116acc6af.title: Headlamp
ed27f5e2-cac5-4a32-a5d9-49f116acc6af.description: Let there be visibility! Connect to a trigger to turn on and off. Adjustable beam range.

695d66c8-b937-472d-8bc2-f3d72dd92879.title: Warehouse Spotlight
695d66c8-b937-472d-8bc2-f3d72dd92879.description: Let there be visibility! Connect to a trigger to turn on and off. Adjustable beam range.

dfefc9d7-db03-4d25-ad85-eae1d824d8c0.title: Radio
dfefc9d7-db03-4d25-ad85-eae1d824d8c0.description:
All hits, all the time. Those beastly bots have hijacked and are now transmitting classic selections from their deeply unusual taste in music. Activate it by interacting with it
or by connecting it to a trigger.

818f4e15-ff51-4fed-b874-723a25d62e1c.title: Horn
818f4e15-ff51-4fed-b874-723a25d62e1c.description: Add it to your vehicle or use it as a door bell. Honk at your friends to avoid accidents. Set the pitch and connect it to a trigger to activate it.

42786777-c148-4e13-9bab-e460564e79c3.title: Seat
42786777-c148-4e13-9bab-e460564e79c3.description: Used for avoiding standing. Take a seat and relax or add it to your vehicle so your friends can tag along. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the seat.

ca003562-fde7-463c-969e-f8334ae54387.title: Toilet
ca003562-fde7-463c-969e-f8334ae54387.description: Used for avoiding standing. Take a seat and relax or add it to your vehicle so your friends can tag along. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the toilet. Donâ€™t forget to flush!

161786c1-1290-4817-8f8b-7f80de755a06.title: Totebot Head: Bass
161786c1-1290-4817-8f8b-7f80de755a06.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this

4c6e27a2-4c35-4df3-9794-5e206fef9012.title: Totebot Head: Percussion
4c6e27a2-4c35-4df3-9794-5e206fef9012.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this

a052e116-f273-4d73-872c-924a97b86720.title: Totebot Head: Synth Voice
a052e116-f273-4d73-872c-924a97b86720.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this

1c04327f-1de4-4b06-92a8-2c9b40e491aa.title: Totebot Head: Blip
1c04327f-1de4-4b06-92a8-2c9b40e491aa.description: This robot head is broken. But the sound generator inside seems to still be working. Creative mechanics can probably find a way to make music with this

3efe715f-8745-475f-a609-5e7cbe09a8ef.title: Bathtub
3efe715f-8745-475f-a609-5e7cbe09a8ef.description: Used for maximum relaxation. Sit down and relax or add it to your vehicle to stay nice and clean on the go. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the bathtub.

9f0f56e8-2c31-4d83-996c-d00a9b296c3f.title: Logic Gate
9f0f56e8-2c31-4d83-996c-d00a9b296c3f.description: The Logic Gate is a powerful block that allows you to build basic logical functions. By pressing E on the block, the mechanic can choose between different logic gate types. The logic gate can be connected to other logic gates, triggers, timers and more. Great for making advanced creations.

8f7fd0e7-c46e-4944-a414-7ce2437bb30f.title: Timer
8f7fd0e7-c46e-4944-a414-7ce2437bb30f.description: The Timer allows you delay the interaction between two interactive parts. For example, between a switch and a controller. It goes great with Logic Gates.

38ee0516-abc5-4e46-9195-c763610d7ec4.title: Driver's Saddle
38ee0516-abc5-4e46-9195-c763610d7ec4.description: Makes bearings turn left and right. Can be connected to an engine to control the direction of travel. Can also be connected to triggers that can be activated from the saddle.

20f59114-5964-451f-bb47-820da3ebbc3b.title: Saddle
20f59114-5964-451f-bb47-820da3ebbc3b.description: Used for avoiding standing. Take a seat and relax or add it to your vehicle so your friends can tag along. Can be connected to triggers which can activate other interactive parts from the saddle.

8c7efc37-cd7c-4262-976e-39585f8527bf.title: Connect Tool
8c7efc37-cd7c-4262-976e-39585f8527bf.description: Every mechanic's favorite tool. Connects interactive parts together, for example: a gas engine to bearings or a thruster to a driver's seat.

ed185725-ea12-43fc-9cd7-4295d0dbf88b.title: Sledgehammer
ed185725-ea12-43fc-9cd7-4295d0dbf88b.description: This mighty sledgehammer will let you push loose items around by hitting them.

5cc12f03-275e-4c8e-b013-79fc0f913e1b.title: Lift
5cc12f03-275e-4c8e-b013-79fc0f913e1b.description: Build on the lift to create freely movable constructions that won't be fixed to the ground. Can be elevated and lowered as well as lift creations that have flipped over.

43562d7c-d1a8-4cea-98e0-ad791320729b.title: Lift
43562d7c-d1a8-4cea-98e0-ad791320729b.description: Build on the lift to create freely movable constructions that won't be fixed to the ground. Can be elevated and lowered as well as lift creations that have flipped over.

c60b9627-fc2b-4319-97c5-05921cb976c6.title: Paint Tool
c60b9627-fc2b-4319-97c5-05921cb976c6.description: Paint any part or block to personalize your creations or even make beautiful art! Paint using the left mouse button and delete with the right. Press 'Q' to open the color selector. Simply hold down left mouse button and drag if you want to paint larger surfaces.

fdb8b8be-96e7-4de0-85c7-d2f42e4f33ce.title: Weld Tool
fdb8b8be-96e7-4de0-85c7-d2f42e4f33ce.description:
Weld your creations together!
Select the Weld Tool and left-click on a loose creation, then left-click on a surface of another creation to weld them together. You can also join touching parts on the lift. Hold the left mouse button on the first part and drag to the part you wish to weld together.

3384010e-bc1c-42bb-83ef-dbc78a1f9636.title: Handbook
3384010e-bc1c-42bb-83ef-dbc78a1f9636.description: Contains all the information you need to learn how to build amazing machines and become a true Scrap Mechanic.

4152ce33-9b43-4c51-80a3-e0b4fe38841d.title: Raft Shark Mount
4152ce33-9b43-4c51-80a3-e0b4fe38841d.description:
A plastic shark mount prop from the survival game Raft.
It seems to have some mechanical joints inside. Maybe it can bite?

448f7c93-699d-47b4-8e3e-296971067ef4.title: Spudgun
448f7c93-699d-47b4-8e3e-296971067ef4.description: The potato shooting spud gun is great for protecting yourself in dangerous situations. It can even break weaker block materials

0229f59d-1ba3-446a-8f9c-df8b0f816e51.title: Mountable Spudgun
0229f59d-1ba3-446a-8f9c-df8b0f816e51.description:
The potato shooting mountable spud gun is great for protecting your creations.
Connect it to a trigger that is connected to a seat to shoot while seated.

24001201-40dd-4950-b99f-17d878a9e07b.title: Large Explosive Canister
24001201-40dd-4950-b99f-17d878a9e07b.description:
Highly explosive canister that can detonate by strong collisions or by Spud Guns
This canister has a large explosion radius

8d3b98de-c981-4f05-abfe-d22ee4781d33.title: Small Explosive Canister
8d3b98de-c981-4f05-abfe-d22ee4781d33.description:
Highly explosive canister that can detonate by strong collisions or by Spud Guns
This canister has a small explosion radius

7700c1f2-a33a-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002.title: Printer Tool
7700c1f2-a33a-11ea-bb37-0242ac130002.description: Build on the lift to create freely movable constructions that won't be fixed to the ground. Can be elevated and lowered as well as lift creations that have flipped over.
